Introduction

Davin is a South Korean trainee under One Cool Jacso Entertainment. He debuted as a member of the boy group XODIAC on April 25, 2023.

On February 2, 2024, One Cool Jacso Entertainment announced that Davin would be taking a break for two months for personal reasons
